; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN\">设某个大学要创建一个学生信息数据库</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">StuInfo</FONT></SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN\'>，</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN\">该数据库中要用来存储学校所有学生的详细信息。你是该大学的数据库管理人员，你须创建该数据库并对其进行规范的管理。</SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: \"Arial\",\"sans-serif\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"\'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoNormal style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 14pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><SPAN style=\'FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"\'>学生数据库要求：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NumList style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: 36.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<SPAN style=\'FONT: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>新数据库名为 </SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">StuInfo</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NumList style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: 36.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<SPAN style=\'FONT: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>该数据库应该包含一个数据文件和一个日志文件，逻辑名称分别</SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">StuInfo </FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>和 </SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">StuInfo</FONT></SPAN></B><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>_Log</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>。这些文件默认是创建在 C:\\Program Files\\Microsoft SQL Server\\MSSQL.1\\MSSQL\\Data 文件夹中。<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=NumList style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: 36.0pt\"><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol\"><SPAN style=\"mso-list: Ignore\">·<SPAN style=\'FONT: 7pt \"Times New Roman\"\'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>要求</SPAN></B><SPAN style=\'FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; mso-ansi-language: ZH-CN\'>数据文件应放在d:\\SQL。日志文件应放在e:\\SQL。（<B style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><SPAN style=\"COLOR